\n\nJulie wants to read half of the remaining pages tomorrow:\n\\[\n\
\\frac{84}{2} = 42 \\text{ pages}\n\\]\n\nThus, the number of pages Julie \
should read tomorrow is:\n\\[\n\\boxed{42}\n\\]Let the number of large \
