month = 2 * $600 = $1200\n\nTherefore, Noah's sales for this month are \
**$1200**.To find out how many of Mr. Sanchez's students received a final \
grade of B and above, we can follow these steps:\n\n1. Determine the number \
of students who got a final grade below B:\n   - 40% of 60 students = 0.40 \
\[Times] 60 = 24 students.\n\n2. Subtract the number of students who got \
