\\[\n5x = 100\n\\]\n\nTo find \\( x \\), divide both sides by 5:\n\n\\[\nx = \
\\frac{100}{5} = 20\n\\]\n\nThus, Alyssa ate \\( \\boxed{20} \\) chicken \
nuggets.To find the total number of beetles eaten each day, we can follow \
