\n   - With 30 snakes, the total number of birds eaten per day is:\n     \\[\n\
     30 \\text{ snakes} \\times 3 \\text{ birds/snake} = 90 \\text{ birds}\n  \
   \\]\n\n3. **Determine the number of beetles eaten by the birds**:\n   - \
Each bird eats 12 beetles per day.\n   - With 90 birds, the total number of \
