\\text{ beetles/bird} = 1080 \\text{ beetles}\n     \\]\n\nThe total number \
of beetles eaten each day is **1080 beetles**.To find out how many ounces of \
soda Peter bought, we first determine how much money he spent.\n\n1. He \
started with $2.00 and left with $0.50.\n2. The amount he spent is:\n   \\[\n \
  2.00 - 0.50 = 1.50\n   \\]\n\n3. The cost of soda is $0.25 per ounce. We \
