Total time = 4 hours (initial) + 2 hours (with 8 people) = 6 hours\n\nFinal \
answer: **6 hours**To find out how many people were on the ship the monster \
ate in the first hundred years, we can set up the problem as follows:\n\n1. \
Let \\( x \\) be the number of people on the ship that was consumed in the \
first hundred years.\n2. Each subsequent ship has twice as many people as the \
