\\text{width} \\times \\text{height} = 4 \\, \\text{ft} \\times 6 \\, \
\\text{ft} \\times 3 \\, \\text{ft} = 72 \\, \\text{cubic feet}\n\\]\n\nNext, \
determine how much water Nancy initially fills the aquarium with:\n\n\\[\n\
