feet}\n\\]\n\nThus, the final amount of water in the aquarium is:\n\n\\[\n\
\\boxed{54} \\text{ cubic feet}\n\\]First, let's find the length of Jamie's \
last name, \"Grey.\" \n\n1. \"Grey\" has 4 letters.\n2. Since Bobbie's last \
