> sequence[i + 1] for i in range(len(sequence) - 1))\n\n# Example usage:\n\
sequence = [5, 3, 2, 1]\nprint(has_decreasing_trend(sequence))  # Output: \
True\n\nsequence = [5, 4, 5, 3]\nprint(has_decreasing_trend(sequence))  # \
