are the tuples you want to compare. \\n- The function returns `True` if all \
elements in `tuple2` are greater than the corresponding elements in `tuple1`, \
and `False` otherwise.\\n\\n### Example:\\n```python\\nresult = \
check_tuples((1, 2, 3), (2, 3, 4))  # This will return True\\nresult = \
