2. \\( a + c > b \\)\n3. \\( b + c > a \\)\n\nHere's a simple Python function \
that implements this logic:\n\n```python\ndef is_valid_triangle(a, b, c):\n   \
 return a + b > c and a + c > b and b + c > a\n\n# Example usage:\n\
