so:\\n\\\\[\\nW_2 = W_1 - 7 = 27 - 7 = 20 \\\\text{ kg}\\n\\\\]\\n\\nNow, let \
\\\\( W_3 \\\\) and \\\\( W_4 \\\\) be the weights lost by the two remaining \
people, who lost the same amount:\\n\\\\[\\nW_3 = W_4 = x\\n\\\\]\\n\\nThe \
