butcher\[CloseCurlyQuote]s delivery arrived at dusk. If all the ground beef \
delivered by the three butchers weighed 100 pounds, how many packages did the \
third butcher deliver?\""}, {
              StyleBox["\"Response:\"", Bold, StripOnInput -> False], 
              "\"Let \\\\( x \\\\) be the number of packages delivered by the \
third butcher.\\n\\nThe weights of the packages from each butcher are as \
follows:\\n- First butcher: \\\\( 10 \\\\) packages \\\\( \\\\times 4 \\\\) \
