**Regular hours per day:** 8 hours\\n2. **Overtime hours per day:** 10 hours \
- 8 hours = 2 hours\\n3. **Hourly wage:** $18.00\\n4. **Overtime pay rate:** \
$18.00 + ($18.00 / 2) = $18.00 + $9.00 = $27.00\\n\\nNow, calculate her total \
earnings:\\n\\n- **Regular pay for 8 hours per day for 5 days:**\\n  - 8 \
hours/day * $18.00/hour * 5 days = $720.00\\n\\n- **Overtime pay for 2 hours \
per day for 5 days:**\\n  - 2 hours/day * $27.00/hour * 5 days = \
$270.00\\n\\nFinally, add the regular pay and the overtime pay:\\n\\n- \
